{"tid":1602934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警阻被截查者用手機　RTHK攝影質問期間遭警棍擊中手部","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:18.000Z","uid":261852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b826f347a50efae4fb91ff293148e472f621362","tid":1602934,"uid":261852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483244-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483244-20190929.htm&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=ce440e49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483244-20190929.htm&h=60653ecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483244-20190929.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大批防暴警察傍晚在銅鑼灣及灣仔一帶進行驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n在灣仔修頓球場附近，防暴警員截查兩名黑衣女子，並喝斥二人不可使用手機，一名女警一度欲搶去其中一人的手機，喝令二人關機。<br />\n<br />\n本台攝影助理拍攝過程，並追問警員有何權力要求被捕者關手機，隨即遭警員推撞，並被質問是否想「妨礙司法公正」，期間本台攝影助理被警棍打中手部，手指紅腫及一度難以伸直。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台發言人表示，今晚本台攝影助理在正常採訪拍攝期間遭阻撓及手部被警棍擊傷。香港電台嚴厲譴責此等針對新聞記者之暴力行為，並保留追究權利。"},{"pid":"fe2e8edad42f8236f21ba378a0b13724f168f8bf","tid":1602934,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"521521c5c71d4fe97113d62a49132c61df321f32","tid":1602934,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a7d3cb1afb68a0bc0892385aba35f300bf1790","tid":1602934,"uid":286966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"